  <span id="freeText14050556511707749917" style="display:none">Review of Kindle edition<br />Publication date: February 14, 2012<br />Publisher: Howard Books<br />Language: English<br />ASIN: B005WK6JFI<br />388 pages<br /><br />If you are a Christian who believes that the Bible is the word of God, then believing in demons intellectually is easy. Believing in their physical presence in the world is harder. If you have been trained in logic, skepticism, science and a general dismissing of superstition, believing in the physical presence of demons in this world is even harder. In this novel Peretti hits the reader in the face with demons and their existence and power in the physical world. A well written, chilling read.</span>
